verses.text_plain: O Lord, rebuke me not in thine anger, neither chasten me in thy hot displeasure.
verses.verse_html:
1O Lord, rebuke me not in thine anger, neither chasten me in thy hot displeasure. ▼
▼ chief…: or, overseer
 , ▼
▼ Sheminith: or, the eighth

footnotes.body_html: ▼ Sheminith: or, the eighth

verses.text_plain: Have mercy upon me, O Lord; for I am weak: O Lord, heal me; for my bones are vexed.
verses.verse_html: 2Have mercy upon me, O Lord; for I am weak: O Lord, heal me; for my bones are vexed.

verses.text_plain: My soul is also sore vexed: but thou, O Lord, how long?
verses.verse_html: 3My soul is also sore vexed: but thou, O Lord, how long?

verses.text_plain: Return, O Lord, deliver my soul: oh save me for thy mercies’ sake.
verses.verse_html: 4Return, O Lord, deliver my soul: oh save me for thy mercies’ sake.

verses.text_plain: For in death there is no remembrance of thee: in the grave who shall give thee thanks?
verses.verse_html: 5For in death there is no remembrance of thee: in the grave who shall give thee thanks?

verses.text_plain: I am weary with my groaning; all the night make I my bed to swim; I water my couch with my tears.
verses.verse_html:
6I am weary with my groaning; all the night make I my bed to swim; I water my couch with my tears. ▼
▼ all…: or, every night

footnotes.body_html: ▼ all…: or, every night

verses.text_plain: Mine eye is consumed because of grief; it waxeth old because of all mine enemies.
verses.verse_html: 7Mine eye is consumed because of grief; it waxeth old because of all mine enemies.

verses.text_plain: Depart from me, all ye workers of iniquity; for the Lord hath heard the voice of my weeping.
verses.verse_html: 8Depart from me, all ye workers of iniquity; for the Lord hath heard the voice of my weeping.

verses.text_plain: The Lord hath heard my supplication; the Lord will receive my prayer.
verses.verse_html: 9The Lord hath heard my supplication; the Lord will receive my prayer.

verses.text_plain: Let all mine enemies be ashamed and sore vexed: let them return and be ashamed suddenly.
verses.verse_html: 10Let all mine enemies be ashamed and sore vexed: let them return and be ashamed suddenly.
